snippet.title: Rocket League® - OMG It Has Everything!
snippet.description: COMING JULY 7: Rocket League explodes onto PS4 and PC! Four-player splitscreen, eight-player online, an all-new Season mode, full Battle-Car customization with more than 10 billion possible combinations, and true PS4/ PC cross-platform play only scratch the surface of what Rocket League has to offer. Plus, as an added bonus, PlayStation 4 users have exclusive access to Twisted Metal's own Sweet Tooth as a playable vehicle!
